  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4466190/extras/f9c8aa664b54f9b490b87cadd29fa42d.poster.avif?t=1773730980\" aria-label=\"Sugar glider soaring through the ocean near jellyfish, coral and starfish.\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4466190/extras/f9c8aa664b54f9b490b87cadd29fa42d.webm?t=1773730980\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4466190/extras/f9c8aa664b54f9b490b87cadd29fa42d.mp4?t=1773730980\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as Wattle, a sugar glider under the ocean!  Explore the great barrier reef as you acquire aquatic allies to cure coral colonies.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">Satisfying 3d platforming</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4466190/extras/3fedb3e13c61e6bb8d02173edaf77ef7.poster.avif?t=1773730980\" aria-label=\"Sugar glider jumping on jellyfish and gliding through bubbles.\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4466190/extras/3fedb3e13c61e6bb8d02173edaf77ef7.webm?t=1773730980\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4466190/extras/3fedb3e13c61e6bb8d02173edaf77ef7.mp4?t=1773730980\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Run, jump and glide through underwater environments.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">Save the reef</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4466190/extras/75d4bbabf8ac09672da7bfd9286eb04c.poster.avif?t=1773730980\" aria-label=\"Sugar glider bringing a fish to dead coral, returning colour in a burst of sparkles.\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4466190/extras/75d4bbabf8ac09672da7bfd9286eb04c.webm?t=1773730980\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4466190/extras/75d4bbabf8ac09672da7bfd9286eb04c.mp4?t=1773730980\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Seek out lost fish and use them to rejuvenate dying coral colonies.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">Grow your entourage</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4466190/extras/c69fb3643c184fc3d6ab74d282e46659.poster.avif?t=1773730980\" aria-label=\"Sugar glider next to large blue fish.\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4466190/extras/c69fb3643c184fc3d6ab74d282e46659.webm?t=1773730980\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4466190/extras/c69fb3643c184fc3d6ab74d282e46659.mp4?t=1773730980\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The more coral you save, the more friendly fish will join you on your journey.  With more allies in your swarm, you can jump higher and access more areas in the environment!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">Developed by 4 people</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Brought from nothing to release in 5 weeks by the 4-person  Down Underwater team at the Screen Queensland Games Residency in Brisbane, Australia.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Music in gameplay trailer credit:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Adventures in Adventureland</i> Kevin MacLeod  Licensed under Creative Commons: By Attribution 4.0 </p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4466190/extras/f9c8aa664b54f9b490b87cadd29fa42d.poster.avif?t=1773730980\" aria-label=\"Sugar glider soaring through the ocean near jellyfish, coral and starfish.\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4466190/extras/f9c8aa664b54f9b490b87cadd29fa42d.webm?t=1773730980\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4466190/extras/f9c8aa664b54f9b490b87cadd29fa42d.mp4?t=1773730980\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as Wattle, a sugar glider under the ocean!  Explore the great barrier reef as you acquire aquatic allies to cure coral colonies.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">Satisfying 3d platforming</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4466190/extras/3fedb3e13c61e6bb8d02173edaf77ef7.poster.avif?t=1773730980\" aria-label=\"Sugar glider jumping on jellyfish and gliding through bubbles.\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4466190/extras/3fedb3e13c61e6bb8d02173edaf77ef7.webm?t=1773730980\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4466190/extras/3fedb3e13c61e6bb8d02173edaf77ef7.mp4?t=1773730980\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Run, jump and glide through underwater environments.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">Save the reef</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4466190/extras/75d4bbabf8ac09672da7bfd9286eb04c.poster.avif?t=1773730980\" aria-label=\"Sugar glider bringing a fish to dead coral, returning colour in a burst of sparkles.\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4466190/extras/75d4bbabf8ac09672da7bfd9286eb04c.webm?t=1773730980\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4466190/extras/75d4bbabf8ac09672da7bfd9286eb04c.mp4?t=1773730980\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Seek out lost fish and use them to rejuvenate dying coral colonies.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">Grow your entourage</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4466190/extras/c69fb3643c184fc3d6ab74d282e46659.poster.avif?t=1773730980\" aria-label=\"Sugar glider next to large blue fish.\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4466190/extras/c69fb3643c184fc3d6ab74d282e46659.webm?t=1773730980\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4466190/extras/c69fb3643c184fc3d6ab74d282e46659.mp4?t=1773730980\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The more coral you save, the more friendly fish will join you on your journey.  With more allies in your swarm, you can jump higher and access more areas in the environment!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">Developed by 4 people</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Brought from nothing to release in 5 weeks by the 4-person  Down Underwater team at the Screen Queensland Games Residency in Brisbane, Australia.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Music in gameplay trailer credit:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Adventures in Adventureland</i> Kevin MacLeod  Licensed under Creative Commons: By Attribution 4.0 </p>",
